name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`CREATE_MAN`,
t1.`CREATE_TIME`,
t1.`DEPENDENCIES`,
t1.`ID`,
t1.`MERGE_SYSTEM_ID`,
t11.`MARKET_URL` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_MARKET_URL`,
t11.`NAME` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_NAME`,
t11.`PRODUCT_GROUP_ID` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_PRODUCT_GROUP_ID`,
t11.`PRODUCT_ID` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_PRODUCT_ID`,
t21.`DIGEST` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_SOURCE_DIGEST`,
t1.`MERGE_SYSTEM_SOURCE_ID`,
t21.`NAME` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_SOURCE_NAME`,
t21.`OSS_FILE` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_SOURCE_OSS_FILE`,
t11.`SYSTEM_TAG` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_TAG`,
t11.`SYSTEM_TAG2` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_TAG2`,
t11.`SYSTEM_TAG3` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_TAG3`,
t11.`SYSTEM_TAG4` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_TAG4`,
t11.`TYPE` AS `MERGE_SYSTEM_TYPE`,
t1.`NAME`,
t1.`ORDER_VALUE`,
t1.`SETTINGS`,
t1.`SYSTEM_ID`,
t1.`UPDATE_MAN`,
t1.`UPDATE_TIME`,
t1.`VALID_FLAG`,
t1.`VER`
FROM `SYSTEM_MERGE` t1 
LEFT JOIN `SYSTEM` t11 ON t1.`MERGE_SYSTEM_ID` = t11.`ID` 
LEFT JOIN `SYSTEM_SOURCE` t21 ON t1.`MERGE_SYSTEM_SOURCE_ID` = t21.`ID`
